---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Twisted Oak Taxidermy" description="Meet Austin, the taxidermist behind Twisted Oak Taxidermy in Mount Airy, NC. Licensed for regular and avian taxidermy.">
  <section class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-charcoal text-center mb-12">
        About Twisted Oak
      </h1>

      <div class="prose-custom space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-4">The Taxidermist</h2>
          <p class="text-earth leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Twisted Oak Taxidermy is run by Austin, a licensed taxidermist based in Mount Airy, North Carolina.
            Licensed for both regular and avian taxidermy, Austin brings a hands-on, detail-oriented approach
            to every piece that comes through the shop.
          </p>
          <p class="text-earth leading-relaxed mb-4">
            What started as a passion for the outdoors turned into a craft — and then a business. Every mount
            that leaves Twisted Oak is built to last and designed to capture the moment your trophy was taken.
          </p>
          <p class="text-earth leading-relaxed">
            Austin is also an entrepreneur at heart, always looking for ways to grow and serve the community.
            When he's not in the shop, you'll find him outdoors, working with his hands, or helping other small
            businesses get off the ground.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-4">Why "Twisted Oak"?</h2>
          <p class="text-earth leading-relaxed">
            The name comes from the character of the land here in Surry County — old oak trees shaped by
            wind and time, still standing strong. That's the spirit behind the work: natural, rugged, built to last.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-4">Service Area</h2>
          <p class="text-earth leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Based in Mount Airy, NC, we serve hunters and outdoor enthusiasts across the region:
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
            {["Mount Airy, NC", "Pilot Mountain, NC", "King, NC", "Elkin, NC", "Dobson, NC", "Surry County, NC", "Stuart, VA", "Galax, VA"].map((area) => (
              <div class="bg-cream rounded px-3 py-2 text-sm text-earth-dark text-center">
                {area}
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="text-earth text-sm mt-4">
            Don't see your area? We accept specimens from anywhere. Shipping and long-distance drop-off available — <a href="/contact" class="text-tan-dark hover:text-tan underline">contact us</a> for details.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="text-center py-8">
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-charcoal hover:bg-charcoal-light text-cream px-8 py-3 rounded font-heading font-semibold tracking-wide transition-colors inline-block">
            Get in Touch
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
